Monday Skins League
Our Monday night skins league is open to everyone who can hit the ball. NO PROS! We want to keep this fair for everyone. There will be an online leaderboard updated after every round; at the end of the season ( 6 Months ) we will crown a winner to receive a free Club 100 membership.
